00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:33.010
The cool thing we
introduced in this release

00:01:33.010 --> 00:01:36.370
is that you can add a Click
Listener to these polygons.

00:01:36.370 --> 00:01:38.560
So for example, if
the user clicked

00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:40.980
on the polygon around
Googleplex, then

00:01:40.980 --> 00:01:42.850
your app could
automatically zoom

00:01:42.850 --> 00:01:47.130
into the entire area you have
defined for that polygon.

00:01:47.130 --> 00:01:50.960
So this brings user
interactions to the next level.

